metadata.name: Four Floors of Claws
metadata.description:
The Four Floors of Claws is the first Masterwork of @BabySynthetic.

A piece designed entirely inside Dalle-2 from his past 5 months works.

A single cohesive artwork of entirely generative images seamlessly woven together telling the story from the center outwards.

Covering a variety of topics, we find our hero Niko, the cat in the center of a universe of shapes colors and sounds, all infused with iconography from his early works, and set in a future Singapore landscape where the cats are in charge, and only the new Cat Queen of Chinatown has a say in what goes on.

This 1/1 artwork was created in Dalle-2 at 10000 x 10000 px ( 1:1 aspect ratio).
